Package io.dvlopt.linux.io

Class LinuxIO

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.dvlopt.linux.io.LinuxIO

  • public class LinuxIO
extends java.lang.Object
    Class containing static methods and constants for performing basic native IO.

    The API is kept close to what LibC offers so that users can easily write higher level constructs.

    See Also:
    LibC low-level IO
